Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:44.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}For you！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我想好好回應你
